data.description: Enter this sweet home, crossing the threshold into the bright foyer which has nice stone flooring! The living room is open to the dining room offering a great space for family and friends to dine together! The kitchen has a large work island as well as new vinyl plank wood flooring which also extends into the den! The cozy den has a great gas fireplace adding a warm and welcoming ambience! The main bedroom is sizeable and comfortable with beautiful wood flooring! The main bath has a large garden tub and double vanity! There is a third bedroom at the opposite side of the house giving privacy to teens, visitors, etc. The laundry room is large enough for storing items and there is an a great attached workshop! All this and a swimming pool and large, fenced-in lot...plenty of room for throwing a baseball, football, frisbe, etc.! This home is located on a cul-de-sac and minutes away from grocery stores, parks, restaurants, and much more!
